data.description: This home qualifies for 12k in grant funds and 6% interest from our preferred lender. One-level living at its finest ! This fabulous and spacious home is great for growing families or those looking for a forever home. When you enter the home you will be greeted to a large living room with a cozy brick fireplace and open concept in the dining room and kitchen! The kitchen features granite countertops, gas stove, stainless steel appliances, a spacious pantry, lots of cabinets and large drawers for storage and more! There is a huge yet cozy den with a wood burning fireplace off the living room that is currently being used as a playroom. In addition there is a sitting area off the master bedroom that could serve as an extra bedroom, office or music/entertainment room! The MBR features French doors, sitting area & awesome master bath and laundry closet. The back yard and covered patio are well maintained, private and perfect for entertaining!
